---
// src/components/RealityCheck.astro
---

<section class="py-32 bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-200" id="timeline">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-6">
        Real talk: Good things take time.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Most agencies promise you the moon overnight. We prefer to tell you the truth. 
        Here is exactly what happens after we shake hands.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-24">

      <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 relative overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-slate-200/50 transition-all duration-500">
        <span class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 text-[180px] font-bold text-slate-50 opacity-50 select-none group-hover:text-slate-100 transition-colors">
            1
        </span>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
                    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-300"></span>
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400">Month 1</span>
                </div>
                
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">We plant the seeds.</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-7">
                    We build your engine and introduce your 800+ new pages to Google. Itâ€™s brand new, so nobody knows it exists yet. It's quiet.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-slate-100">
                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">What you see</p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-900 font-medium">
                    <i data-lucide="minus" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-300"></i>
                    Silence.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 relative overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-slate-200/50 transition-all duration-500">
        <span class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 text-[180px] font-bold text-slate-50 opacity-50 select-none group-hover:text-blue-50 transition-colors">
            2
        </span>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
                    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500 animate-pulse"></span>
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-600">Month 2-3</span>
                </div>
                
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Google checks you out.</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-7">
                    Google notices the new pages but checks if you are the real deal. They send a few visitors your way to test if they find what they need.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-slate-100">
                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">What you see</p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-900 font-medium">
                    <i data-lucide="trending-up" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500"></i>
                    First visitors.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 relative overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-slate-200/50 transition-all duration-500">
        <span class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 text-[180px] font-bold text-slate-50 opacity-50 select-none group-hover:text-emerald-50 transition-colors">
            3
        </span>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
                    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span>
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-600">Month 4+</span>
                </div>
                
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">The floodgates open.</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-7">
                    You passed the test. Google starts ranking you at the top for neighborhoods across the city. Traffic flows, and you own the map.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-slate-100">
                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">What you see</p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-900 font-medium">
                    <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500"></i>
                    Steady Leads.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center border-t border-slate-200 pt-20">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-slate-900 leading-normal">
            "If you need customers <span class="text-slate-400 line-through decoration-slate-300">tomorrow</span>, buying ads is faster.<br class="hidden md:block" />
            If you want customers <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold border-b-2 border-blue-600 pb-0.5">forever</span> without paying for clicks, we build this."
        </h3>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>